      "text": "LizNoirのプロデュ―サー、姫野と言います\nいつかは、莉央達がお世話になったそうで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Kiriko Himeno‚ LizNoir’s producer.\nI heard you helped out Rio and the girls recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.50484733678199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ\nむしろ、お邪魔になってしまったのではないかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ not at all.\nIf anything‚ I got in their way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "お互い、決勝で会えるように頑張りましょう\n長瀬麻奈ちゃんのためにも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s both do our best to meet again in the finals.\nIn honor of Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
