      "text": "（寮に戻って軽くお祝いを済ませると、みんなは）\n（パソコンでグランプリ予選の感想を調べ始めた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After returning to the dorms and having a light celebration‚)\n(the girls begin to look up the reactions to the Grand Prix preliminary round on the computer.)",
