      "text": "どう？　私の評判は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well? What are they saying about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.864847374929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんはねー\n……特にないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What they’re saying about you‚ Suzu…\n…is nothing in particular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.86625324981712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
